      "value": "<p>Your body knits back together especially quickly while you are resting.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Con 13.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong>: You regain twice as many Hit Points when taking an 8-hour rest. In addition, for each uninterrupted 8 hours of rest you receive, you recover from @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.Item.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P]{Afflictions} as though you had rested for a full day. This effect does not stack with other effects that increase these rates of healing and recovery; if more than one would apply, you choose which one takes effect.</p>"
